Six Schedule in Manipur Hills is pending overdue. All successive GoM ignore for decades and the result is with Naga & Kuki movement as well as the Manipuri movement. However, for the cause of peace KNO has retracted to TC. Hence, to curb with all these demands, Manipur state has to quickly implement Six Schedule in the Hill Districts of Manipur if it ever wants peace in the state. The state authority should be strong and trustworthy in the implementation so as to gain back the trust from the Hill People who are deprived economically comparing to its tribal counterparts of Assam, Tripura, Mizoram & Meghalaya who all are enjoying the Six schedule of the Constitution of India. The majority Meiteis in general should also support like its 4 counterpart states.
